object.script:
samples = {}
tick = 1 iter = 1 tickStart = 1
fuelD = 0 fuelDOld = 0 fuelA = 0 fuelAOld = 0 speedA = 0 speedAOld = 0
rate1 = 0 rate2 = 0 time = 0 range = 0
start = false
function onTick() fuel = math.max(input.getNumber(1), 0) speed = math.abs(input.getNumber(2))
sampleMax = property.getNumber("Sampling time")
if tickStart < 60 then tickStart = tickStart+1 end
if not start and tickStart >= 60 and fuel > 0 then start = true for i = 1,sampleMax do samples[i] = {} samples[i][1] = fuel samples[i][2] = 0 end fuelA = fuel fuelAOld = fuel end
if start then if tick > 60 then fuelAOld = fuelA fuelDOld = fuelD speedAOld = speedA speedA = 0 fuelA = 0
tick = 0
samples[iter][1] = fuel samples[iter][2] = speed
for i in pairs(samples) do fuelA = fuelA + samples[i][1] speedA = speedA + samples[i][2] end fuelA = fuelA/sampleMax speedA = speedA/sampleMax fuelD = fuelAOld - fuelA
iter = iter+1 if iter > sampleMax then iter = 1 end end
tick1 = tick/60 rate1 = math.max(fuelDOld*(1-tick1)+fuelD*tick1, 0) fuelALerp = math.max(fuelAOld*(1-tick1)+fuelA*tick1, 0) speedALerp = math.max(speedAOld*(1-tick1)+speedA*tick1, 0)
if rate1 > 0.001 then time = math.min(fuelALerp/(rate1*60), 1000) range = math.min(speedALerp*time*0.06, 10000) else time = 0 range = 0 end
if speed > 1 then rate2 = rate1*1000/speed else rate2 = 0 end
tick = tick+1 end
output.setNumber(1, rate1) output.setNumber(2, rate2) output.setNumber(3, math.floor(time)) output.setNumber(4, math.floor(range)) end

i,o,m = input,output,math pgn,pgb,gn,gb,sn,sb = property.getNumber,property.getBool,i.getNumber,i.getBool,o.setNumber,o.setBool
t1,fuel1,fuelOld,dist1,cons,consOld = 0,0,0,0,0,0 init = 0
samples = {} sampleIter = 1 sampleMax = pgn("Consumption sampling time")
function onTick() fuel = gn(1) speed = m.abs(gn(2))
reset = gb(1)
if init > 60 then if reset then samples = {} fuel1,dist1,t1,cons,consOld = 0,0,0,0,0 elseif t1 <= 60 then fuel1 = fuel1+m.max(fuelOld-fuel,0) dist1 = dist1+speed/60 t1 = t1+1 else consOld = cons if fuel1 > 0 and dist1 > 1 and speed > 1 and fuel > 0 then samples[sampleIter] = fuel1*1000/dist1 cons = 0 for i = 1,sampleMax do cons = cons+(samples[i] or 0) end cons = cons/sampleMax if sampleIter < sampleMax then sampleIter = sampleIter+1 else sampleIter = 1 end end fuel1,dist1,t1 = 0,0,0 end else init = init+1 end
consSm = cons*t1/60+consOld*(1-t1/60)
fuelOld = fuel
sn(1,consSm) end

s,scr,i,o,m=self,screen,input,output,math pgn,pgb,gn,gb,sn,sb=property.getNumber,property.getBool,i.getNumber,i.getBool,o.setNumber,o.setBool sc,dl,drf=scr.setColor,scr.drawLine,scr.drawRectF pi2,abs=m.pi*2,m.abs
delta = pgn("Fill rate") th = pgn("Line thickness") wd = pgn("Line width")
function line(r,g,b) return{r=r,g=g,b=b,x=0, fill=function(s,on) if on then s.x = m.min(s.x+delta,wd) else s.x = m.max(s.x-delta,0) end sc(r,g,b) drf(16-m.floor(s.x),0,2*m.floor(s.x),th) end } end
function turn(r,g,b,left) return{r=r,g=g,b=b,x=2*wd, fill=function(s,on) if on and s.x == 2*wd then s.x = 0 end s.x = m.min(s.x+delta,2*wd) sc(r,g,b) if left then drf(m.min(16,16-s.x+wd),0,-m.min(s.x,wd*2-s.x),th) else drf(m.max(16,16+s.x-wd),0,m.min(s.x,wd*2-s.x),th) end end } end
line1 = line(20,0,0) line2 = line(255,255,255) line3 = line(255,0,0) turn1 = turn(150,50,0,false) turn2 = turn(150,50,0,true)
function onTick() left = gb(1) right = gb(2) rev = gb(4) mark = gb(5) stop = gb(3) or gb(6) end
function onDraw() line1:fill(mark) turn1:fill(left) turn2:fill(right) line2:fill(rev) line3:fill(stop) --[[
if right and x2 == width*2 then x2 = 0 end x2 = m.min(x2+delta,width*2) sc(150,50,0) drf(width-x2,0,m.min(x2,width),thic)
if left and x3 == width*2 then x3 = 0 end x3 = m.min(x3+delta,width*2) sc(150,50,0) drf(m.max(width,x3),0,x3,thic) ]] end
